<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.886199>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Vanmanenia orcicampus ı mouth. aı CMK 22732 ı 20.6 mm SL; bı CMK 22732 ı 22.1 mm SL; and cı MHNG 2767.094 ı holotypeı 47.5 mm SL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/886199/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.886197>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Vanmanenia orcicampus ı CMK 22732 ı paratypes; Laos: Nam Ngum on Plain of Jars; aı 20.6 mm SL (reversed); and bı 23.2 mm SL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/886197/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.886201>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Nam Ngum at Ban Khangviangı Xiangkhouang Provinceı Laos; type locality of Vanmanenia orcicampus. Juveniles were found among the pebbles and cobble in the foreground rightı adult among the bamboos of the weir." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/886201/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

